        <h2>Russian Visa</h2>
        <p>
            Family and friends travelling to Russia for the Games must apply for a tourist VISA.  Please read through the following sections carefully in order to apply for your VISA.  Those applying for visas should always refer to the latest information on the Russian Embassy website (http://www.rusembassy.ca/node/400). 
        </p>
        <p>
            Please note that the Consular section of the Russian Embassy in Ottawa, Montreal and Toronto will no longer accept applications. Only applications made IN PERSON to the Visa Application Centers in Ottawa, Montreal and Toronto are at the present time accepted. 
        </p>
       
